title: El Huddle: Winners and Losers of the Trade Deadline, and talking Raiders, Comedy, and Identity with Anjelah Johnson-Reyes
itunes:title: El Huddle: Winners and Losers of the Trade Deadline, and talking Raiders, Comedy, and Identity with Anjelah Johnson-Reyes
description:
Will Selva and MJ Acosta-Ruiz discuss who made the most (and least) noise at the Trade Deadline and how the new players might impact week 9. Then they’re joined by comedian, actress, and author Anjelah Johnson-Reyes to talk about her time as a Raiderette, her road into comedy, and her journey defining her identity.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
